                    <span>Thomas and Grace West translate Plato's Euthyphro, Apology and Crito and Aristophanes' Clouds in a clear and modern fashion. The useful background information and clear footnotes help make this an important book to have if  you want to read about Socrates. This book is a "must have" for  any Socrates fan indeed!</span>
                  
